The biology and some population parameters of the grasshopper, Ronderosia bergi, 
under laboratory conditions.

Mariottini Y(1), de Wysiecki ML, Lange C.

Author information:
(1)Centro de Estudios Parasitológicos y de Vectores (CEPAVE - CCT La Plata 
